    "monster5149": "<h1 class=monster>Goblin Cutthroat<br><span class=type>Small natural humanoid</span><br><span class=level>Level 1 Skirmisher<span class=xp> XP 100</span></span></h1><table class=bodytable><tr><td><b>HP</b> 30; <b>Bloodied</b> 15<td class=rightalign><b>Initiative</b> +5<tr><td><b>AC</b> 15, <b>Fortitude</b> 13, <b>Reflex</b> 14, <b>Will</b> 13<td class=rightalign><b>Perception</b>+2<tr><td><b>Speed</b> 6<td class=rightalign>Low-light vision<tr><td colspan=2></table><h2>Standard Actions</h2><p class='flavor alt'>(⚔) <b>Short Sword</b> ✦ <b>At-Will</b></p><p class=flavorIndent><i>Attack:</i> Melee 1 (one creature); +6 vs. AC</p><p class=flavorIndent><i>Hit:</i> 1d6 + 5 damage, or 2d6 + 5 if the goblin has combat advantage against the target. In addition, the goblin can shift 1 square.</p><p class='flavor alt'>➶ <b>Dagger</b> ✦ <b>At-Will</b></p><p class=flavorIndent><i>Attack:</i> Ranged 10 (one creature); +6 vs. AC</p><p class=flavorIndent><i>Hit:</i> 1d4 + 5 damage.</p><h2>Move Actions</h2><p class='flavor alt'> <b>Deft Scurry</b> ✦ <b>At-Will</b></p><p class=flavorIndent><i>Effect:</i> The goblin shifts up to 3 squares.</p><h2>Triggered Actions</h2><p class='flavor alt'> <b>Goblin Tactics</b> ✦ <b>At-Will</b></p><p class=flavorIndent><i>Trigger:</i> The goblin is missed by a melee attack.</p><p class=flavorIndent><i>Effect (Immediate Reaction):</i> The goblin shifts 1 square.</p><p class='flavor alt'><b>Skills</b> Stealth +8, Thievery +8<br> <b>Str</b> 13 (+1)                <b>Dex</b> 17 (+3)                <b>Wis</b> 14 (+2)<br><b>Con</b> 14 (+2)                <b>Int</b> 8 (-1)                <b>Cha</b> 8 (-1)</p><p class=flavor><b>Alignment</b> evil       <b> Languages</b> Common, Goblin<br><b>Equipment</b>: dagger x2, leather armor , light shield , short sword .</p><p class=publishedIn>Published in Dungeon Magazine 180, Monster Vault, page(s) 154, Dungeon Magazine 205, Dungeon Magazine 211, Dungeon Magazine 220, Dungeon Magazine 221.</p>",
